spec_data.Name: perl-Test-ConsistentVersion
spec_data.Description:
The purpose of this module is to make it easy for other distribution
authors to have consistent version numbers within the modules (as well as
readme file and changelog) of the distribution.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 04:44:41 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Ensures a CPAN distribution has consistent versioning
